## 1. Design Intent

- Create a contemporary mountain cabin organized around panoramic views, warm materials, a compact two-level plan, and a large outdoor terrace.
- Prioritize clear day/night/service zoning, resilient mountain-weather detailing, and simple circulation between the interior living spaces and terrace.
- Keep the documentation suitable for preliminary planning and professional review only.

