## 18. Architect Review Checklist

- Confirm room program, room areas, and circulation strategy.
- Confirm terrace zoning, guard concept, waterproofing strategy, and drainage strategy.
- Confirm facade material logic, opening sizes, safety glass needs, and thermal-performance targets.
- Confirm roof geometry, drainage, snow guards, penetrations, and eaves.
- Confirm accessibility, fire-safety, and local planning constraints.
- Confirm that all drawings and documents remain marked PRELIMINARY until properly reviewed and approved through real processes.

